text: Lily Jane Collins (born 18 March 1989) is an English actress and model. She played Collins Tuohy in The Blind Side. She also played Rosie Dunne in Love, Rosie in 2014. Collins was born in Surrey, England. She is the daughter of drummer Phil Collins. ==References== Category:English television actors Category:English movie actors Category:1989 births Category:Living people
